No. 13,

Original.

Texas v. New Jersey et al. Richard. W. Ervin, Attorney General of Florida, and Fred M. Burns, Assistant Attorney General, on the motion. [For earlier orders herein, see 369 U. S. 869; 370 U. S. 929; 371 U. S. 873; 372 U. S. 926, 973.]

The report of the Special Master is received and ordered filed. The motion of the State of Florida for leave to intervene is granted.
